snippet.title: Seven Deadly Sins: Origin - Official G-STAR 2023 Trailer
snippet.description:
Dive into the world of The Seven Deadly Sins: Origin to see various threats you'll face and more in this open-world action-adventure RPG. In The Seven Deadly Sins: Origin, explore various locations of the continent and collect Star Fragments. Form your own combat style by collecting heroes from The Seven Deadly Sins and Four Knights of the Apocalypse manga and anime series. The Seven Deadly Sins: Origin is coming to PC, mobile, and console.

#Gaming #GameTrailers
